node.text:
The GLOCK MOS. Allowing for quick sight acquisition of your target.

#MOS #G45MOS #GLOCK #GLOCKon

Team GLOCK ladies take the lead at the USPSA Area 5 Championship in Lexington, KY this past weekend!

@scuzi23 won High Lady in Production Division with her G34 and @ashley_rheuark won High Lady in Carry Optics Division with her G34 Gen5 MOS. 

With the USPSA Nationals upcoming, this competition helped prep the team's performance.

Great win Michelle & Ashley! 👊💥

#ThisIsTeamGLOCK #GLOCKcompete #CompetitiveShooting

node.text:
Introducing the GLOCK 35th Anniversary Watch.

This solar powered chronograph uses a sapphire glass, is water resistant to 10 ATM, and has an elegant mesh band along with a secondary silicone band. The watch is a limited production exclusive, contains classic GLOCK pistol design elements, and has been tested and proven by GLOCK engineers. 
Perfection inspired Precision.

Click the link in our bio to order yours today!

#GLOCKprecision #GLOCKwatch #watch #GLOCKon #precision

@glockprecision
